Gold for Immediate Delivery Surpasses $1,920 an Ounce, Reaching New Record

-- B y   G l e n y s   S i m
-- 
2011-09-06T05:49:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/gold-advances-to-a-record-as-european-debt-concern-boosts-demand-for-haven.html
Gold for immediate delivery gained
as much as 1 percent to an all-time high of $1,920.25 an ounce,
surpassing the previous peak of $1,913.50 reached on Aug. 23.
December-delivery futures on the Comex in  New York  climbed to a
record $1,923.10 an ounce, up 2.5 percent from their close on
Sept. 2.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Glenys Sim at 
 gsim4@bloomberg.net  